comment: Proving ~ axc11r from ~ axc11 . The hypotheses are two instances of ~ axc11 used in the proof here. Some systems introduce ~ axc11 as an axiom, see for example System S2 in https://us.metamath.org/downloads/finiteaxiom.pdf . By contrast, this database sees the variant ~ axc11r , directly derived from ~ ax-12 , as foundational. Later ~ axc11 is proven somewhat trickily, requiring ~ ax-10 and ~ ax-13 , see its proof. (Contributed by Wolf Lammen, 18-Jul-2023.)
